": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 357, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "dd7ad6d4-7c37-4807-bff2-afeff2b9d2ef": {"__data__": {"id_": "dd7ad6d4-7c37-4807-bff2-afeff2b9d2ef", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "f66b03e4-84e7-4971-9c6e-c86263689be4", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bafd03d29670dc90ee6ebc101c218609bf0effcc397f2e3fd1bb79da5c2bec29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0af52393-add0-4695-9573-268c70b772a6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "24571bea6a17f8786627eb568cff6c8b209c3d473f54737729c60a5f3cd4d339", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "f154343b-d6ca-4a5c-a3b8-4ab7328a4f26", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a50ce3982a2bded1be60ebf8d4784e17119d1e03df4c79f3ecc9130605694560", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Together \u201c the Parties \u201d\n\nWHEREAS THE PARTIES CONFIRM THAT:\n\nThe prospective applicant is seeking to refer to data that the data owner owns;\nThe  prospective  applicant  is  seeking  to  do  so  for  a  purpose  under  the  Biocidal  Products  Regulation 528/2012 (\u201c the BPR \u201d);", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 358, "end_char_idx": 636, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "f154343b-d6ca-4a5c-a3b8-4ab7328a4f26": {"__data__": {"id_": "f154343b-d6ca-4a5c-a3b8-4ab7328a4f26", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "f66b03e4-84e7-4971-9c6e-c86263689be4", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bafd03d29670dc90ee6ebc101c218609bf0effcc397f2e3fd1bb79da5c2bec29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "dd7ad6d4-7c37-4807-bff2-afeff2b9d2ef", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23b4d08db288b127e7f7bdaaa6e6de3fdf5db73b48648b41d6913e14ec27375", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "87e880dc-fecf-4279-80fc-2095dd1b6ced", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "09e69e1a6a6bfc4eb4d7559453836d79030c90e9e173e24488913442fcc08fe0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The  data  owner  is  under  an  obligation  in  certain  circumstances  to  share  data  with  the  prospective applicant and may in any event choose to do so regardless of that obligation;\nThe Parties are entering into data sharing negotiations;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 639, "end_char_idx": 886, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "87e880dc-fecf-4279-80fc-2095dd1b6ced": {"__data__": {"id_": "87e880dc-fecf-4279-80fc-2095dd1b6ced", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "f66b03e4-84e7-4971-9c6e-c86263689be4", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bafd03d29670dc90ee6ebc101c218609bf0effcc397f2e3fd1bb79da5c2bec29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "f154343b-d6ca-4a5c-a3b8-4ab7328a4f26", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a50ce3982a2bded1be60ebf8d4784e17119d1e03df4c79f3ecc9130605694560", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "7350c033-e180-47ab-a4cd-b7fdcfce7d6f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3d985ff1011703598b12ddc11b6f270895adda0f32a74168c8b0d19887911af0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "A  non-disclosure  agreement  is  necessary  to  reassure  the  Parties  that  the  use  to  which  any  information exchanged  or  otherwise  disclosed  during  the  negotiations  will  be  limited  to  the  legitimate  purpose  as established in the BPR;\n\nTHE PARTIES HAVE THEREFORE AGREED AS FOLLOWS:\n\n1.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 889, "end_char_idx": 1196, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "7350c033-e180-47ab-a4cd-b7fdcfce7d6f": {"__data__": {"id_": "7350c033-e180-47ab-a4cd-b7fdcfce7d6f", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "f66b03e4-84e7-4971-9c6e-c86263689be4", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bafd03d29670dc90ee6ebc101c218609bf0effcc397f2e3fd1bb79da5c2bec29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "87e880dc-fecf-4279-80fc-2095dd1b6ced", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "09e69e1a6a6bfc4eb4d7559453836d79030c90e9e173e24488913442fcc08fe0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "5c9c2467-f2b4-4510-b4ac-d6ba6f4c5cc2", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "486aaa194100bb5d4792294da2d15466bda497691098acef14a0c4386448d08d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Disclosure of Information\n\na.\n\n A Party may disclose to the other Party information with a view to negotiating the sharing of data for a purpose under  the BPR (\u201c the Purpose \u201d).   The Parties agree that the terms and conditions set forth in  this Agreement shall govern any such disclosure of information.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1197, "end_char_idx": 1503, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "5c9c2467-f2b4-4510-b4ac-d6ba6f4c5cc2": {"__data__": {"id_": "5c9c2467-f2b4-4510-b4ac-d6ba6f4c5cc2", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "f66b03e4-84e7-4971-9c6e-c86263689be4", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bafd03d29670dc90ee6ebc101c218609bf0effcc397f2e3fd1bb79da5c2bec29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "7350c033-e180-47ab-a4cd-b7fdcfce7d6f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3d985ff1011703598b12ddc11b6f270895adda0f32a74168c8b0d19887911af0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "117f74bd-648c-4696-a780-bec422ac79c7", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "beaae68c9c2a5e479b535ad509a50b845a84f290da21e9273e1ce395fb130779", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "All information disclosed by a Party or by Affiliates of a Party to the other Party or its respective Affiliates  orally,  electronically,  writing  or  by  any  other  means  during  the  data  sharing negotiations  shall  be  considered  as  confidential  unless  expressly  stated  otherwise  by  the disclosing  Party.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1507, "end_char_idx": 1829, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "117f74bd-648c-4696-a780-bec422ac79c7": {"__data__": {"id_": "117f74bd-648c-4696-a780-bec422ac79c7", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "f66b03e4-84e7-4971-9c6e-c86263689be4", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bafd03d29670dc90ee6ebc101c218609bf0effcc397f2e3fd1bb79da5c2bec29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "5c9c2467-f2b4-4510-b4ac-d6ba6f4c5cc2", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "486aaa194100bb5d4792294da2d15466bda497691098acef14a0c4386448d08d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "957fe07e-5935-4f02-86d0-021acd353c48", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eddc5d6a0760515220055f5419c1a185511fc879bb148525e5c4d26ba09588f6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "All  such  confidential  information  shall  be  referred  to  hereinafter  as \" \".  Information shall also include the identity of the Parties, the contents of this agreement and the fact that they have entered into this Agreement.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1835, "end_char_idx": 2067, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "957fe07e-5935-4f02-86d0-021acd353c48": {"__data__": {"id_": "957fe07e-5935-4f02-86d0-021acd353c48", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "f66b03e4-84e7-4971-9c6e-c86263689be4", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bafd03d29670dc90ee6ebc101c218609bf0effcc397f2e3fd1bb79da5c2bec29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "117f74bd-648c-4696-a780-bec422ac79c7", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "beaae68c9c2a5e479b535ad509a50b845a84f290da21e9273e1ce395fb130779", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "aac4e848-40a4-4855-b017-0c27fbe827c9", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b34166883e4be24375ac421b60334558e2c72a8963d78f219aee94e1b739185c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "NON-DISCLOSURE / CONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENT\n\nb. The  Information,  including  any  material  support  containing  Information,\n\n  will  remain  the exclusive property of the disclosing Party and the receiving Party will not acquire any right, title, license or interest on or to the Information.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2069, "end_char_idx": 2363, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "aac4e848-40a4-4855-b017-0c27fbe827c9": {"__data__": {"id_": "aac4e848-40a4-4855-b017-0c2