: "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u201c \u201d shall mean any company controlling, controlled by, or under common control with a Party to this Agreement, control meaning in this context the direct or indirect ownership of more than fifty percent (50%) of the voting stock/shares of a company, or the power to nominate more  than  half  of  the  directors,  or  the  power  otherwise  to  determine  the  policy  of  a company or organisation.\n\n2.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2551, "end_char_idx": 2954, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "3d63df17-71a1-4c20-88c2-6d23bd4bf6fa": {"__data__": {"id_": "3d63df17-71a1-4c20-88c2-6d23bd4bf6fa", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "f66b03e4-84e7-4971-9c6e-c86263689be4", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bafd03d29670dc90ee6ebc101c218609bf0effcc397f2e3fd1bb79da5c2bec29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0e5b33e3-264d-43e1-87b0-a04011918de2", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5e3dc9fa03072f94b28343b7204a8ad90d302577c576259a6352c2e7beeec65a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a45c940f-20e2-4170-9829-8e306062ec81", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "fb0c32ad410e709486517ee3d0580cfc21da4c4b6497d6d97af776cf90effc0a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Use of Information\n\na.\n\n The receiving Party undertakes not to use the Information  disclosed to it for  any purpose except  the  Purpose.  This  Agreement  does  not  constitute  a  license  by  implication  or otherwise to use the Information commercially or otherwise.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2955, "end_char_idx": 3226, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_te